            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped vegetables</strong> to a baking tray</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 3 or more? Use two trays!</p><p>Drizzle with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and season with a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for an initial 10-15 min or until everything is starting to soften</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2452Step-4-x200.jpg",
