            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst everything is cooking, combine your <strong>mayo</strong> with your <strong>mustard ketchup</strong> and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> in a small bowl – this is your<strong> sweet mustard mayo</strong></p>",
